Package: simplebf
Type: Package
Title: Simple functions for Bayes Factor tests in restricted conditions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dan MacLean
Maintainer: Dan MacLean <dan.maclean@tsl.ac.uk>
Description: Calculate Bayes Factor t-tests from tidy dataframes in a simple declarative manner.
    Ideal for basic use of Bayes Factors in simple cases. Wraps methods in BayesFactor 
